text: Emphytoecia lineolata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Blanchard in Gay in 1851. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Emphytoecia lineolata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1851
title: Emphytoecia lineolata
